1. **Njihovoj** kući je bio najlepši vrt u celom kraju. (Their house had the most beautiful garden in the entire area.)
2. *Njihovoj* deci je bilo dozvoljeno da ostanu budni do kasno sinoć. (*Their* children were allowed to stay up late last night.)
3. Oni su došli u posetu *njihovoj* rodbini u Srbiji. (They came to visit *their* relatives in Serbia.)
4. *Njihovoj* firmi je trebalo nekoliko meseci da se oporavi nakon finansijske krize. (*Their* company needed several months to recover after the financial crisis.)
5. Zadovoljni su svojim rezultatima na poslednjem testu, ali *njihovoj* oceni je nedostajao jedan bod za odličan uspeh. (They were satisfied with their results on the last test, but *their* grade was one point short of excellent.)
6. *Njihovoj* ljubavi nije bilo granica, čak ni nakon mnogo godina braka. (*Their* love knew no bounds, even after many years of marriage.)
7. Kada su stigli u kamp, prvo su postavili svoj šator pored *njihovog*. (When they arrived at the campsite, they first set up their tent next to *theirs*.)
8. Bila je srećna kada je videla da je u prodavnici bilo nekoliko novih knjiga u *njihovoj* kolekciji. (She was happy when she saw that there were several new books in *their* collection at the store.)
9. Učenici su otišli u obilazak grada sa *njihovim* nastavnikom istorije. (The students went on a city tour with *their* history teacher.)
10. Iako su živeli daleko jedno od drugog, *njihova* prijateljstva je opstalo kroz godine. (Although they lived far apart, *their* friendship persisted over the years.)